window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>If you want to learn how to speak Spanish with complete confidence without having to relocate to a Spanish-speaking country for months or even years, then this audiobook is for you.</p> <p>The biggest mistake language learners make is studying boring, complex grammar material that causes them to fall asleep before speaking a single word! The problem with most phrase books is that they are teaching the wrong phrases, or at least a lot of uncommon phrases. This audiobook is full of the most common phrases you will use while speaking Spanish.</p> <p>Designed as a quick reference tool and an easy-to-use study guide, this inexpensive and up-to-date audiobook offers fast, effective communications. The perfect companion for tourists and business travelers in Spain and Latin America, it features words, phrases, and sentences that cover many of the expressions you’ll use daily.</p> <p>You will find:</p> <ul> <li>Over 50 hours of Spanish audio lessons</li> <li>A system that will allow you to master conjugating Spanish verbs</li> <li>Native Spanish-speaking voice actor to make sure you develop an authentic Spanish accent</li> <li>How to construct proper sentences</li> <li>How you should use articles, adjectives, verbs, adverbs, nouns, pronouns, conjunctions, tenses, numbers, and other elements</li> <li>Awesome short stories, including English version, vocabulary, and quizzes</li> <li>How to create everyday conversations, ask and answer questions, speak about sports, music, clothes, foods, drinks, etc</li> <li>How to identify and fix your own mistakes</li> <li>Spanish short stories to learn and grow your vocabulary the fun way</li> <li>Powerful tips for success</li> <li>And much more!</li> </ul> <p>If you want to converse fluently in Spanish in no time, then get this audiobook, and start learning today!</p>"; 
